Package com.camerontec.catalys.core.session.persistence

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IFIXSessionStatePersister
    This interface defines how a session persists FIX messages (outbound and, optionally, inbound) and session state using any generic persistence mechanism.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BatchedPersistedInMessageIterator
    Iterates over persisted in messages.
    BatchedPersistedMessageIterator
    Iterates over persisted messages.
    BatchedPersistedOutMessageIterator
    Iterates over persisted out messages.
    JournalingPersister
    Journaling FIX session state persister implementation.
    MemoryPersister
    Memory based implementation of the IFIXSessionStatePersister interface.
    MemorySeqNoOnlyPersister
    Memory based implementation of the IFIXSessionStatePersister interface which only saves sequence numbers and session state.
    PersisterBenchmark
    Measures the performance of a persister object.
